  <name>Serigy</name>
  <summary>Manage your clipboard minimally</summary>
  <description>
    <p>A minimalist clipboard manager that captures your copies and keeps only what matters.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Automatic background capture</li>
      <li>Limited slots to keep only what matters</li>
      <li>Pin favorites so they don't get replaced</li>
      <li>Incognito mode to pause monitoring</li>
      <li>Global shortcut for quick access</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <developer_name translate="no">Cleo Menezes Jr.</developer_name>

